## Engines

| DDGS function | Available backends |
| --------------|:-------------------|
| text()        | `bing`, `brave`, `duckduckgo`, `google`, `grokipedia`, `mojeek`, `startpage`, `yandex`, `yahoo`, `wikipedia`|
| images()      | `bing`, `duckduckgo` |
| videos()      | `duckduckgo` |
| news()        | `bing`, `duckduckgo`, `yahoo` |
| books()       | `annasarchive` |

